data.description: One owner home conveniently located in Rose Rock Estates. Larger Franklin floor plan with split floor plan and several upgrades. Eat in kitchen features sleek and stylish subway tile backsplash, cabinet hardware, upgraded faucet with soap dispenser and nice sized pantry. Spacious primary bedroom and ensuite with upgraded tile shower and soaking tub. Large walk-in closet. Home is equipped with security system, keyless entry door, and camera operated doorbell. Upgraded 10x14 concrete patio. Seller offering floor allowance to replace carpet if desired with acceptable offer.
